{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01BNLkFwt6aBc2ybCDAwHXhh","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01UnDiRseJeBHRQqA8hrQ93s","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__persistence__roster__quarkus__jakarta/run_2/output/CHANGELOG.md","content":"# Migration Changelog: Quarkus to Jakarta EE\n\n## [2026-03-17T02:40:00Z] [info] Project Analysis\n- Identified Quarkus 3.30.5-based sports roster management application\n- Application manages Leagues (Summer/Winter), Teams, and Players with many-to-many relationships\n- 12 Java source files, 1 Dockerfile, 1 pom.xml, 1 application.properties\n- Quarkus-specific dependencies: quarkus-hibernate-orm, quarkus-jdbc-h2, quarkus-smallrye-health, quarkus-arc, quarkus-resteasy-jackson, quarkus-junit5\n- Application uses: CDI (@ApplicationScoped, @Inject), JAX-RS (@Path, @GET, @POST, @DELETE), JPA (EntityManager, CriteriaBuilder), @Transactional\n- Entity classes already use jakarta.persistence.* imports (Quarkus 3.x uses Jakarta namespace)\n- RequestBean already uses jakarta.ws.rs.*, jakarta.enterprise.*, jakarta.inject.*, jakarta.transaction.*\n- JPA metamodel classes (Player_, Team_, League_) generated by hibernate-jpamodelgen\n\n## [2026-03-17T02:41:00Z] [info] Migration Strategy Decision\n- Target runtime: Open Liberty (full Jakarta EE 10 implementation)\n- Rationale: Open Liberty is a mature, lightweight Jakarta EE runtime with full support for CDI, JAX-RS, JPA, JTA\n- JPA provider changes from Hibernate (Quarkus) to EclipseLink (Open Liberty default)\n- JSON serialization changes from Jackson (Quarkus) to JSON-B (Jakarta EE standard)\n- Application packaging changes from uber-jar (Quarkus) to WAR (Jakarta EE standard)\n\n## [2026-03-17T02:42:00Z] [info] Smoke Test Generation\n- Created smoke.py with 81 test assertions covering all REST endpoints\n- Tests cover: CRUD for leagues, teams, players; relationship management; complex queries by position, salary, league, city, sport\n- Tests use Python urllib for HTTP requests (no external dependencies)\n\n## [2026-03-17T02:43:00Z] [info] pom.xml Migration\n- Changed groupId from quarkus.tutorial to jakarta.tutorial\n- Changed artifactId from roster-quarkus to roster-jakarta\n- Changed packaging from default (jar) to war\n- Removed all Quarkus dependencies: quarkus-hibernate-orm, quarkus-jdbc-h2, quarkus-smallrye-health, quarkus-arc, quarkus-resteasy-jackson, quarkus-junit5\n- Removed Quarkus BOM and dependency management (Netty, Vert.x CVE fixes no longer needed)\n- Removed Quarkus Maven plugin, native profile\n- Added Jakarta EE 10 API (provided scope)\n- Added H2 database driver (bundled in WAR)\n- Added Hibernate JPA metamodel generator (compile-time annotation processing)\n- Configured maven-compiler-plugin with annotationProcessorPaths for metamodel generation\n- Added maven-war-plugin with failOnMissingWebXml=false\n- Added liberty-maven-plugin for Open Liberty integration\n\n## [2026-03-17T02:44:00Z] [info] Open Liberty server.xml Configuration\n- Created src/main/liberty/config/server.xml\n- Enabled jakartaee-10.0 feature (includes CDI 4.0, JAX-RS 3.1, JPA 3.1, JTA, etc.)\n- Configured HTTP endpoint on port 8080\n- Configured webApplication with contextRoot=\"/\" and third-party API visibility\n- Configured H2 DataSource with JNDI name jdbc/RosterDS\n- Used JdbcDataSource driver class for H2 connection\n\n## [2026-03-17T02:44:30Z] [info] JPA persistence.xml Configuration\n- Created src/main/resources/META-INF/persistence.xml\n- Configured RosterPU persistence unit with JTA transaction type\n- Referenced jdbc/RosterDS JNDI data source\n- Listed all 5 entity classes (League, SummerLeague, WinterLeague, Team, Player)\n- Set drop-and-create schema generation (matching original Quarkus configuration)\n\n## [2026-03-17T02:45:00Z] [info] JAX-RS Application Class\n- Created src/main/java/quarkus/tutorial/roster/RosterApplication.java\n- Extends jakarta.ws.rs.core.Application with @ApplicationPath(\"/\")\n- Required for Jakarta EE WAR deployment to register JAX-RS resources\n\n## [2026-03-17T02:45:30Z] [info] CDI beans.xml Configuration\n- Created src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/beans.xml\n- Set bean-discovery-mode=\"all\" for full CDI scanning\n- Required for @ApplicationScoped bean discovery in standard Jakarta EE\n\n## [2026-03-17T02:46:00Z] [info] RequestBean Refactoring\n- Replaced @Inject EntityManager with @PersistenceContext(unitName = \"RosterPU\") EntityManager\n- Standard Jakarta EE pattern for container-managed EntityManager injection\n- Removed jakarta.inject.Inject import (no longer needed for EntityManager)\n\n## [2026-03-17T02:46:30Z] [info] application.properties Update\n- Replaced Quarkus-specific configuration with comments pointing to new configuration locations\n- All Quarkus properties (datasource, hibernate-orm, http.port) now handled by server.xml and persistence.xml\n\n## [2026-03-17T02:47:00Z] [info] Dockerfile Migration\n- Replaced single-stage Quarkus Dockerfile with multi-stage build\n- Build stage: maven:3.9.12-eclipse-temurin-21 for WAR compilation\n- Runtime stage: icr.io/appcafe/open-liberty:full-java21-openj9-ubi-minimal\n- Installed Python 3 via microdnf for smoke test execution\n- Copied H2 driver JAR to Liberty's lib directory\n- Copied server.xml to Liberty's config directory\n- Copied WAR to Liberty's apps directory\n- Ran configure.sh for Liberty optimization\n- Changed CMD from mvn quarkus:run to Liberty server run\n\n## [2026-03-17T02:48:00Z] [warning] Docker Image Tag Issue\n- First build attempt: Open Liberty image tag full-java21-openj9-ubi not found\n- Resolution: Changed to full-java21-openj9-ubi-minimal (correct tag for minimal UBI image)\n\n## [2026-03-17T02:48:30Z] [warning] Package Manager Issue\n- Second build attempt: yum not found in ubi-minimal image\n- Resolution: Changed to microdnf (package manager for UBI minimal images)\n\n## [2026-03-17T02:49:00Z] [error] H2 DataSource Connection Failure\n- First runtime: H2 JDBC URL format error with properties.generic configuration\n- Root cause: Liberty's properties.generic element did not correctly pass the URL to H2\n- Resolution: Changed to use jdbcDriver with explicit javax.sql.DataSource class and properties element with lowercase url attribute\n\n## [2026-03-17T02:50:00Z] [error] League Creation Returns 400 Bad Request\n- All league POST requests returned HTTP 400\n- Root cause: JSON-B (Jakarta EE default serializer) requires setters for deserialization; LeagueDetails and TeamDetails had only getters\n- Original Quarkus app used Jackson which can use constructor/field-based deserialization\n- Resolution: Added setter methods to LeagueDetails, TeamDetails, and PlayerDetails\n\n## [2026-03-17T02:51:00Z] [warning] Smoke Test URL Encoding Issue\n- Python urllib rejected URLs with spaces in path segments (e.g., \"/players/position/power forward/name/Jack Patterson\")\n- Resolution: Added urllib.parse.quote() encoding in smoke test request function\n\n## [2026-03-17T02:52:00Z] [info] Final Smoke Test Results\n- All 81/81 test assertions passed\n- Verified: League CRUD, Team CRUD, Player CRUD\n- Verified: Player-Team assignment and removal\n- Verified: Complex queries (by position, salary range, league, city, sport, position+name)\n- Verified: League/sport lookup for players\n- Verified: Team and player deletion\n\n## [2026-03-17T02:52:30Z] [info] Migration Complete\n- Application successfully migrated from Quarkus to Jakarta EE (Open Liberty)\n- All business logic preserved and functional\n- JPA metamodel generation working correctly with Hibernate generator + EclipseLink runtime\n- Docker image builds and runs successfully\n"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":530,"cache_read_input_tokens":117732,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":530,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":2261},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d9729fc2-69e7-40e2-ad86-5630b00c4ba7","uuid":"f961cc0d-6826-4c23-abd7-59fdf38065b3"}
