.xml: CDI bean discovery configuration\n- smoke.py: Comprehensive smoke tests (81 assertions)\n- CHANGELOG.md: Full migration log\n```\n\n### Error Summary\n- **0 critical errors** remaining\n- **3 errors encountered and resolved** during migration:\n  1. Open Liberty Docker image tag (wrong tag name)\n  2. H2 DataSource URL format (Liberty-specific configuration syntax)\n  3. JSON-B deserialization failure (missing setters on DTOs)\n- **2 warnings** encountered and resolved:\n  1. microdnf vs yum for UBI minimal images\n  2. URL encoding for spaces in REST paths (smoke test fix)"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":117,"cache_read_input_tokens":121094,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":117,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":690},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d9729fc2-69e7-40e2-ad86-5630b00c4ba7","uuid":"954aa02d-fabe-4c59-a867-b44661b50684"}
