 smoke.py: Comprehensive smoke tests (81 assertions)\n- CHANGELOG.md: Full migration log\n```\n\n### Error Summary\n- **0 critical errors** remaining\n- **3 errors encountered and resolved** during migration:\n  1. Open Liberty Docker image tag (wrong tag name)\n  2. H2 DataSource URL format (Liberty-specific configuration syntax)\n  3. JSON-B deserialization failure (missing setters on DTOs)\n- **2 warnings** encountered and resolved:\n  1. microdnf vs yum for UBI minimal images\n  2. URL encoding for spaces in REST paths (smoke test fix)","session_id":"d9729fc2-69e7-40e2-ad86-5630b00c4ba7","total_cost_usd":13.970322619999997,"usage":{"input_tokens":11151,"cache_creation_input_tokens":108768,"cache_read_input_tokens":6046199,"output_tokens":31025,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":108768}},"modelUsage":{"aws/claude-3-5-haiku":{"inputTokens":233893,"outputTokens":8523,"cacheReadInputTokens":962659,"cacheCreationInputTokens":66115,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.3643341199999999,"contextWindow":200000},"claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929":{"inputTokens":515,"outputTokens":107,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":0,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.00315,"contextWindow":200000},"aws/claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":11151,"outputTokens":31025,"cacheReadInputTokens":6046199,"cacheCreationInputTokens":108768,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":13.602838500000002,"contextWindow":200000}},"permission_denials":[],"uuid":"cdf7de7c-8582-482b-bd9f-505ecc068caa"}
